instance.name: dim_location
instance.documentation: This is the table to hold data on dim_location.

columns.name: location_id
columns.documentation: The ID of the Shopify POS. This column is the primary key for the locations table. The location_id is null for orders not placed through Shopify POS, such as those placed through the online store.

columns.name: shop_id
columns.documentation: The ID of the store. This column is a foreign key reference to the shop_id column in the shops table.

columns.name: name
columns.documentation: Name of the POS location as provided by the merchant. For example, 150 Elgin Street or Downtown Boutique.

columns.name: created_on
columns.documentation: Date when this shop was created.
